41:31.097 --> 41:35.231
I prize its memory
above all else.

41:35.275 --> 41:38.147
- You've been played.

41:38.191 --> 41:40.759
- Madam Gao can't be trusted.

41:47.156 --> 41:49.898
Killing your wife...

41:52.640 --> 41:54.599
And daughter...

41:54.642 --> 41:57.732
will not bring
my Chico back to me.

41:57.776 --> 42:01.257
But that is not why
we seek revenge, is it?

42:01.301 --> 42:03.695
No.

42:03.738 --> 42:07.481
We merely want to ensure...

42:07.525 --> 42:11.093
that those that wronged us...

42:11.137 --> 42:14.096
suffer...

42:14.140 --> 42:15.141
as we do.

42:15.184 --> 42:16.969
- I didn't tell you
about Maria

42:17.012 --> 42:20.581
because I believed it would
only compound your grief.

42:20.625 --> 42:22.975
Planned to deal
with her myself.

42:23.018 --> 42:26.152
Why make you kill a daughter
to avenge a son?

42:26.195 --> 42:29.068
- You didn't do it
to protect me.

42:29.111 --> 42:32.854
You did it to preserve
your position.

42:37.816 --> 42:40.558
- Run!

42:43.604 --> 42:45.563
- Kill the girl!

